      "content": "idk i feel like i've tried that. but it's like... people just see the avatar or the email or the work output. they don't actually see me. it's not even that it's sad, it's just that it's so empty. if i just stopped showing up... it feels like the world would just keep spinning without a single hiccup. like i'm already basically invisible.",
